==Introduction==
{{Help:Data Model Introduction}}


A large Data Models might be split into multiple files, which might be then imported into the the main model file (see 'import' element below).
The Wiki Automation Tool provides the '''CommonLibraryModel.xml''' file with  common definitions to be shared across all models. '''The CommonLibraryModel.xml file has to be imported in all model files.'''

See [[Help:Package|Package]], [[Help:Concept|Concept]] and [[Help:Property|Property]] pages for further details, how to define Packages, Concepts and Properties.


==Definition==

<pre>
<DataModel>
  <import model="CommonLibraryModel.xml"/>
  <import model="{FILE NAME}"/>

  <concepts>
    <package name="{PACKAGE NAME}" ...>
      <concept name="{CONCEPT NAME}" ...>
        ...
      </concept>
      ...
    </package>
    ...
  </concepts>

  <!-- Property Definitions -->
  <properties>
    <property name="{PROPERTY NAME} ...">
      ...
    </property>
    .....
  </properties>
</DataModel>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {FILE NAME}
| A name of the external file, which contains definitions of the re-usable Concepts and Properties to be imported into this model. The file is searched for in the same folder as main model file and/or in the main folder of Wiki Automation Tool.
|-
! {PACKAGE NAME}
| A name of the Package. See [[Help:Package|Package]] for more details.
|-
! {CONCEPT NAME}
|A name of the Concept. See [[Help:Concept|Concept]] for more details.
|-
! {PROPERTY NAME}
| A name of the Property (or to be more precise Property Definitions). See [[Help:Property|Property]] for more details.
|}


==Semantic database==
The Data Model meta-elements (Data Model itself, Package, Concept) are NOT being defined/represented in the semantic database.


==Example==
<pre>
<DataModel>
  <import model="../../MDA/CommonLibraryModel.xml"/>

  <concepts>
    <package name="Event Management">
      <description>Concepts required to represent information related to AV&amp;V events</description>

      <concept name="Event" plural="Events" type="Dynamic" image="Event.png" color="f9f9f9">
        <structure>
          <property name="Title" mandatory="true"/>
          <property name="Description" mandatory="true"/>
          <property name="Start date"/>
          <property name="End date"/>
        </structure>
      </concept>
    </package>
  </concepts>

  <properties>
    <property name="Description" type="Text" label="Description" attribute="description">
      <description>A free text format to describe the purpose, relevance and functionality of a certain entity.</description>
      <instruction>A "Description" is a text value that reflects a short explanation for a taxonomy element. </instruction>
    </property>
    <property name="End date" type="Date" label="End date" attribute="enddate">
      <description>A date to end an event in a concept.</description>
    </property>
    <property name="Start date" type="Date" label="Start date" attribute="startdate">
      <description>A date to start an event in a concept.</description>
    </property>
  </properties>
</DataModel>
</pre>


